## Gene Details:
- **MSU gene ID:** [LOC_Os06g49450](http://rice.uga.edu/cgi-bin/ORF_infopage.cgi?orf=LOC_Os06g49450)  
- **RAPdb gene ID:** [Os06g0708200](https://rapdb.dna.affrc.go.jp/locus/?name=Os06g0708200)  
- **Gene Symbol:** <u>OsMTOPVIB</u>
- **Genome:**  [MSU7](http://rice.uga.edu/),&nbsp;&nbsp;[IRGSP-1.0](https://rapdb.dna.affrc.go.jp/download/irgsp1.html)
- **Species:** *Oryza sativa*

## Functional Descriptions:
   - **OsMTOPVIB** promotes meiotic DNA double-strand break formation in rice.
   - **OsMTOPVIB** is required for meiotic bipolar spindle assembly.
